==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Anthracene oil
<hw>An"thra*cene oil</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A heavy green oil
(partially solidifying on cooling), which distills over from coal tar at
a temperature above 270⟦deg⟧. It is the principal source of
anthracene.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Anthracic</ent>⟦br⟧
